title: BRIEF-Venator Announces Fourth Quarter Q4 EPS of $0.64
text: 14 AM / Updated 9 minutes ago BRIEF-Venator Announces Fourth Quarter Q4 EPS of $0.64 Reuters Staff Feb 23 (Reuters) - Venator Materials Plc: * VENATOR ANNOUNCES FOURTH QUARTER AND FULL YEAR 2017 RESULTS; REPORTS STRONG EARNINGS AND CASH GENERATION * Q4 ADJUSTED EARNINGS PER SHARE $0.61 * Q4 EARNINGS PER SHARE $0.64 * Q4 REVENUE $528 MILLION * DUE TO 2017 TAX ACT, OTHER INCOME FOR QUARTER, YEAR ENDED DEC 31, 2017 INCREASED BY $34 MILLION * Q4 EARNINGS PER SHARE VIEW $0.59, REVENUE VIEW $543.3 MILLION -- THOMSON REUTERS I/B/E/S Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Bengaluru Newsroom: +1 646 223 8780)
